Now I can't live without you all.

1469
02:10:34.440 --> 02:10:38.990
I want to stay with you all.

1470
02:10:40.210 --> 02:10:44.990
Why leave the house
for my mistake?

1471
02:10:45.780 --> 02:10:51.090
As you say. a wrongdoer
should go.

1472
02:10:52.260 --> 02:10:55.360
I made a mistake.

1473
02:10:55.360 --> 02:10:57.990
I'll leave.

1474
02:10:58.250 --> 02:11:00.660
Abhi!

1475
02:11:02.130 --> 02:11:06.370
- Abhi. don't go. Listen.
- Grandpa needs you all.

1476
02:11:06.370 --> 02:11:09.990
Take good care of him.

1477
02:11:10.210 --> 02:11:12.990
Abhi!

1478
02:11:20.350 --> 02:11:23.980
Listen. don't go. Please.

1479
02:11:47.280 --> 02:11:51.490
You haven't eaten.

1480
02:11:51.500 --> 02:11:54.990
Have this.

1481
02:12:00.090 --> 02:12:03.730
I'll say something.

1482
02:12:03.730 --> 02:12:08.670
My parents showed me your photo.

1483
02:12:08.670 --> 02:12:12.170
I started crying.

1484
02:12:12.170 --> 02:12:18.340
Mom said live as if
a husband is god.

1485
02:12:18.340 --> 02:12:21.510
So I married you.

1486
02:12:21.510 --> 02:12:24.990
Your actions are god's.

1487
02:12:25.080 --> 02:12:30.790
Not once did I think
you made a mistake

1488
02:12:30.790 --> 02:12:33.260
as my God.

1489
02:12:33.260 --> 02:12:36.330
That boy

1490
02:12:36.330 --> 02:12:41.160
came all the way here
to unite us.

1491
02:12:41.160 --> 02:12:46.970
You sent a good boy away
and didn't stop him.

1492
02:12:46.970 --> 02:12:52.940
You're not God. just ordinary.
That's it.

1493
02:12:52.940 --> 02:12:58.350
I want my kids and grand-kids.
I'll live with them.

1494
02:12:58.350 --> 02:13:03.090
Eat. You starved from morning.

1495
02:13:04.150 --> 02:13:06.790
His grandson came?

1496
02:13:06.790 --> 02:13:11.890
So the prince is here.

1497
02:13:11.890 --> 02:13:14.960
This isn't right.

1498
02:13:33.500 --> 02:13:37.220
- Yes. Dad!
- Abhi. I've landed.

1499
02:13:37.220 --> 02:13:39.660
You've won!

1500
02:13:39.660 --> 02:13:42.960
- Dad. - Abhi!

1501
02:13:42.960 --> 02:13:47.090
I feel anxiety now.

1502
02:13:47.150 --> 02:13:52.170
- Yeah.
- I hope Dad's fine.

1503
02:13:52.170 --> 02:13:55.000
Whatever he says.
I'll stay.

1504
02:13:55.000 --> 02:13:58.640
- Where's Grandpa?
- Well. Grandpa...

1505
02:13:58.640 --> 02:14:00.880
You can't talk?

1506
02:14:00.880 --> 02:14:05.520
- Is he near? Call later?
- Dad! It's fine.

1507
02:14:05.520 --> 02:14:08.620
Hospital's ready. yep?

1508
02:14:08.620 --> 02:14:11.950
I'm outside it. You come.

1509
02:14:11.960 --> 02:14:13.760
Bye!

1510
02:14:13.760 --> 02:14:17.900
- Love you!
- Love you too!

1511
02:14:25.230 --> 02:14:29.900
Sorry. Dad! Sorry!

1512
02:14:50.390 --> 02:14:53.090
Brother!

1513
02:15:01.970 --> 02:15:04.090
Brother!

1514
02:15:13.420 --> 02:15:16.490
Brother!

1515
02:15:32.470 --> 02:15:34.700
Indu!

1516
02:15:34.840 --> 02:15:36.990
Indu!

1517
02:15:38.980 --> 02:15:41.090
Indu!

1518
02:15:47.720 --> 02:15:51.090
- Brother! - Hey!

1519
02:15:54.600 --> 02:15:56.950
Brother!

1520
02:16:03.500 --> 02:16:05.500
Brother!

1521
02:16:05.540 --> 02:16:08.900
- Brother! - Indu!

1522
02:16:09.470 --> 02:16:12.990
- Bro! - Hey! Drive.

1523
02:16:13.900 --> 02:16:15.970
Stop!

1524
02:16:31.090 --> 02:16:33.150
Brother!

1525
02:16:41.100 --> 02:16:43.970
Brother!

1526
02:17:20.910 --> 02:17:22.990
Brother!

1527
02:17:23.380 --> 02:17:25.900
Brother!

1528
02:17:30.090 --> 02:17:36.090
Stop. please! I won't repeat it.
Sorry.

1529
02:17:36.960 --> 02:17:40.130
Know who she is?

1530
02:17:40.130 --> 02:17:43.390
She's your sister.

1531
02:17:43.600 --> 02:17:48.990
We're one family. Family!

1532
02:17:59.920 --> 02:18:01.510
Brother!

1533
02:18:01.950 --> 02:18:03.990
Brother!

1534
02:18:06.920 --> 02:18:07.990
Brother!

1535
02:18:07.990 --> 02:18:10.320
- Abhi! - Abhi!

1536
02:18:12.990 --> 02:18:13.990
Bro!

1537
02:18:15.870 --> 02:18:17.200
How dare you.

1538
02:18:17.200 --> 02:18:19.900
Get lost!

1539
02:18:21.600 --> 02:18:25.990
- Hey! - Let him go!

1540
02:18:26.410 --> 02:18:28.950
Tell them. Uncle.

1541
02:18:28.950 --> 02:18:31.990
- Leave him. - Don't hit him.

1542
02:18:33.000 --> 02:18:35.990
Abhi!

1543
02:18:38.650 --> 02:18:40.550
- Indu. - Dad!

1544
02:18:40.550 --> 02:18:45.830
- Brother.
- Uncle. Dad...

1545
02:18:45.830 --> 02:18:48.090
Abhi!

1546
