1550
02:19:12.890 --> 02:19:14.990
Wait.

1551
02:20:00.900 --> 02:20:03.000
Chandra.

1552
02:20:06.910 --> 02:20:09.090
Grandpa.

1553
02:20:37.660 --> 02:20:39.480
<i>Like it or not.</i>

1554
02:20:39.480 --> 02:20:43.470
<i>you're my grandpa;
I'm your grandson.</i>

1555
02:21:57.490 --> 02:22:02.890
Abhi. Abhi! Grandpa is here.

1556
02:22:02.890 --> 02:22:07.100
