1557
02:22:07.100 --> 02:22:11.390
Abhi! Open your eyes.

1558
02:22:11.440 --> 02:22:13.900
Hey!

1559
02:22:13.900 --> 02:22:17.090
Abhi...

1560
02:22:32.650 --> 02:22:37.390
