1567
02:23:01.550 --> 02:23:07.090
I didn't know who you were.

1568
02:23:07.990 --> 02:23:12.620
How'd I fail to know you?

1569
02:23:12.730 --> 02:23:17.790
I hurt my grandson.

1570
02:23:17.800 --> 02:23:20.500
I'm getting old.

1571
02:23:20.500 --> 02:23:26.390
If you try to leave.
I'll hit your legs.

1572
02:23:26.400 --> 02:23:30.110
We'll go home.

1573
02:23:30.110 --> 02:23:33.990
OK. Where's the doctor?

1574
02:23:34.080 --> 02:23:36.990
Doctor!

1575
02:23:52.430 --> 02:23:57.600
Doctor. sir! You're our God.

1576
02:23:57.640 --> 02:24:03.900
You saved our grandson
and made us happy.

1577
02:24:03.900 --> 02:24:07.610
How do I repay your help!

1578
02:24:07.620 --> 02:24:11.710
Sincere thanks.

1579
02:24:11.920 --> 02:24:15.000
Can I take him home-

1580
02:24:24.400 --> 02:24:27.570
Dad. hug me once.

1581
02:24:27.570 --> 02:24:30.990
That's enough!

1582
02:24:36.880 --> 02:24:39.990
My son!

1583
02:24:47.090 --> 02:24:49.990
