village welfare was our welfare.

1587
02:25:10.380 --> 02:25:15.280
My generation is like that.

1588
02:25:15.280 --> 02:25:18.890
But the village is family;

1589
02:25:18.890 --> 02:25:22.960
a united family helps the village.

1590
02:25:22.960 --> 02:25:26.990
My foreign grandson
taught me that.

1591
02:25:29.100 --> 02:25:32.470
Your wishes came true?

1592
02:25:39.040 --> 02:25:45.380
- Hey! Call the American.
- Grandpa! - We'll reject them.

1593
02:25:45.380 --> 02:25:50.700
- Son-in-law! - Yes.
- Ask the priest to wed 3 couples.

1594
02:25:50.700 --> 02:25:52.190
<i>Three weddings?</i>

1595
02:25:52.190 --> 02:25:54.360
Chitra and Bangari!

1596
02:25:54.360 --> 02:25:58.190
Abhi and Satya!

1597
02:25:58.490 --> 02:26:06.930
- Me and Baby. - You'll marry again?
- 60 years again!

1598
02:26:31.890 --> 02:26:37.900
<i>~ In a sky-blue sari
you're like the moon ~</i>

1599
02:26:37.900 --> 02:26:43.960
