1600
02:27:01.820 --> 02:27:07.860
<i>~ In a sky-blue sari
you're like the moon ~</i>

1601
02:27:07.860 --> 02:27:13.840
<i>~ How to reach you? ~</i>

1602
02:27:13.840 --> 02:27:19.650
<i>~ What colour's on your hip?
Will you roll it? ~</i>

1603
02:27:19.650 --> 02:27:25.750
<i>~ How do I get you? ~</i>

1604
02:27:25.750 --> 02:27:31.950
<i>~ Your kisses make me happy;
your hugs excite me ~</i>

1605
02:27:31.950 --> 02:27:37.060
<i>~ In seconds. you slip away ~</i>

1606
02:27:37.060 --> 02:27:40.100
<i>~ You glitter like lightning ~</i>

1607
02:27:40.100 --> 02:27:43.200
<i>~ Your beauty drowns us ~</i>

1608
02:27:43.200 --> 02:27:49.570
<i>~ Everyone in this world
falls for your magic ~</i>

1609
02:27:49.570 --> 02:27:55.500
<i>~ You're my life. village girl ~</i>

1610
02:27:55.500 --> 02:28:02.990
<i>~ With you beside me.
